是这样啊♪ 总觉得你们俩的表情和平时一样沉重，\n我还以为我表达的音乐印象有问题呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"episode086-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"我姑且算是友希那和纱夜\n音乐印象的传达者呢，对吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"episode086-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"纱夜","body":"你的工作没有失误。\n……只是……\n因为乐队还是第一次统一服装","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"episode086-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"纱夜","body":"（凑同学……\n对白金同学说了什么呢……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"episode086-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"不过友希那和纱夜，\n真的都好可爱啊~♪\n两人都很适合呢！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions